:"recXhO6r2ijCY8ekD","ref":"Job.33.5","text":"If thou canst answer me, set thy words in order before me, stand up.","year":-1520},{"id":"recqbrIh6g7jzOoYD","ref":"Job.33.6","text":"Behold, I am according to thy wish in God’s stead: I also am formed out of the clay.","year":-1520},{"id":"recqNdXQFTXyhAjAP","ref":"Job.33.7","text":"Behold, my terror shall not make thee afraid, neither shall my hand be heavy upon thee.","year":-1520},{"id":"recXvU7Bpw8sQ38Qq","ref":"Job.33.8","text":"Surely thou hast spoken in mine hearing, and I have heard the voice of thy words, saying,","year":-1520}]}
